com.bigdata.rdf.rio

Class RDFParserOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.rio.RDFParserOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRDFParserOptions, Serializable

    public class RDFParserOptions
extends Object
implements Serializable, IRDFParserOptions
    Instances of this class may be used to configure options on an RDFParser. The options all have the defaults specified by RDFParserBase.

    Note: synchronization on the class instance is used to ensure safe publication of the member field values.

    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
